These are the components that define the structure of NeXus data files.

 README                    This file
 NeXus.xsd                 XML Schema used to validate NeXus XML data files
 nxdl.xsd                  XML Schema use to validate NeXus NXDL files
 base_classes/             NeXus ratified base class NXDL files
 applications/             instrument and application NXDL files
 contributed_definitions/  NXDL files contributed from community
 manual/                   documentation
 schema/                   XML Schema (XSD) files, as converted from NXDL sources
 test/                     data and examples
 xslt/                     XSLT transformations to convert NXDL into XML Schema (XSD)

--
